                                        650,
                                        2343,
                                        937
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "In this section, as a phenomenological consequence of this model and in particular of the modified algebra (12), we aim to derive the modified Power Spectrum of primordial scalar perturbations during the inflationary epoch. We will partially follow [29] but compute the spectrum through a different method."
                                }
                            ]
